{"tid":2192558,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「她知道，哭是沒有用的。」","createTime":"2020-09-07T08:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T08:11:27.000Z","uid":5655,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"400f2a76a5f5d3683460c391d1e567d71322ab7c","tid":2192558,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"「她知道，哭是沒有用的。」<br />\n<br />\n鍾欣桐為父還債，所以17歲出道，開始了自己的演藝生涯。鍾欣桐最近拍了部片子《情迷黑森林》系列電影時，她晚上和導演在房間排戲，因為太過入戲，她頭不小心撞到床上，立即受傷，血如泉湧。<br />\n<br />\n導演立刻喊停，要送她去醫院。她知道，這一去醫院，勢必要換人，那她的「星途」也許從此就斷了。於是，天真的她對導演說：「要導演陪我排戲不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，她將酒精直接倒在傷口上，再將膠袋包著頭，穿上安全措施繼續拍攝。換了四個袋，倒出四袋血，戲排完時，她幾乎暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n送到醫院，醫生說，再遲來一點，人就玩完了，而且，極有可能得到破傷風。在給她縫針之前，醫生讓他簽生死狀。 在醫生給她縫針時，鍾欣桐就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有打麻醉針，就那樣一針一針地縫著。一個天真的少女，知道自己面對的是怎樣的人生。她知道，哭是沒有用的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48KY4VU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48KY4VU.jpg&h=852a5676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一針，她對醫生說：「我來縫！」醫生看著他，她居然笑了︰「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」<br />\n<br />\n這句話多麼豪邁，在場的人震驚了。因為醫生說，如果熬不過去，她也只有四天的生命了，所以，她願意嘗試生命中不曾嘗試的痛，除了那陳冠希無情的分手，她要給自己縫一針。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sF3SpV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsF3SpV4.jpg&h=aab5d302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從給自己縫針那一天開始，她知道，所有的明天全要靠自己。後來，她一直努力，不停地得獎，終於成為香港最知名，最多人「了解」影星。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2746099/【最緊要人無事】阿嬌鍾欣潼凌晨如廁見暈撞傷眉骨位%20傷口長達6cm接受手術縫數十針\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2746099%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9C%80%E7%B7%8A%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%91%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%8C%E9%8D%BE%E6%AC%A3%E6%BD%BC%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E5%A6%82%E5%BB%81%E8%A6%8B%E6%9A%88%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E7%9C%89%E9%AA%A8%E4%BD%8D%2520%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3%E9%95%B7%E9%81%946cm%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E7%B8%AB%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E9%87%9D&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp3O%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=bb26474e\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2746099/【最緊要人無事】阿嬌鍾欣潼凌晨如廁見暈撞傷眉骨位%20傷口長達6cm接受手術縫數十針</a>"},{"pid":"bb524b9bae7dd2d8765ca74ddfc2595723361097","tid":2192558,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c818c81dde403760e24c53ed77588b034e015f3c","tid":2192558,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">她晚上和導演在房間排戲</span>.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad89c49322b028988bbb04f2b3f4101e824b767e","tid":2192558,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c818c81dde403760e24c53ed77588b034e015f3c","tid":2192558,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">她晚上和導演在房間排戲</span>.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}